flowchart TD
    A[Main conversation] --> B[Claude identifies delegable task]
    B --> C[Launches subagent via Task tool]
    C --> D[New isolated context created]
    D --> E[Subagent receives: system prompt + task]
    E --> F[Subagent works autonomously]
    F --> G[Subagent produces result]
    G --> H[Only result returns to main]
    H --> I[Main context receives summary]
    I --> J[Conversation continues]
